      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">During pediatric rounds, you&#39;re reviewing a case involving hyperbilirubinemia. The attending consultant quizzes the team, asking, &quot;In pediatric patients, what is the foremost reason for undergoing liver transplantation?&quot; How should you respond?</span></span></span></p>",
