      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Match the following clinical findings with their diagnosis<strong>:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cerebellum-web-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/public/images/2024/03/27/picture18_6dgRFdZ.jpg\" style=\"height:124px; width:700px\" /></strong></span></span></p>",
